ca.ualberta.cs.drivr

Class DriversList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.cs.drivr.DriversList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Driver>

    public class DriversList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Driver>
    A class for staring a list of drivers. It is used for tracking the drivers for a request, and enforces the nice property that at any given time at most one driver can have the status of confirmed.
    See Also:
    Driver, RequestState

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  DriversList.ConfirmedDriverAlreadyExistsException
      An exception to be thrown on operations that would break the property of there being at most one confirmed driver.
